    "desc": "AI agents are no longer just for big tech. Small businesses can use them to handle customer support, scheduling, and follow-ups automatically.",
    "keywords": "AI agents for small business, AI automation, business automation, small business AI, AI customer support, AI scheduling, workflow automation",
